      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> 7th level, Ionizing Phased Array</em></p>\n<p>While your ionizing field is active, when you cast a tech power or use a class feature that affects other creatures within the radius of your field, you can choose a number of them equal to 1 + the power's level. The chosen creatures automatically succeed on their saving throws against the power, and they take no damage if they would normally take half damage on a successful save.</p>\n<p>Additionally, when you use your Ionizing Phased Array feature, you create a third blast.</p>",
